                        In the story, &ldquo;<a href="http://www.mediapost.com/publications/article/294406/digital-programmatic-deals-drive-increase-in-loca.html">Digital, Programmatic Deals Drive Increase In Local TV
Ads</a>&rdquo; (February 3, <em>Media Daily News</em>), total local TV advertising projections should have been $20.9 billion in 2017 and $24.2 billion in 2020. For local out of home media it will be
$1.7 billion in 2017.
                    

                    
